# local-only dev / demo / launch artifacts — kept on disk, out of git.
# Whole dirs ignored by path; for individual files, prefix the name with `local.`
# (e.g. docs/local.demo.md) so one pattern covers them without per-file lines.
/Design/
/reports/
**/local.*